e-raggi-x-tutti-numeri-sfida-20973683414.shtml|title=Supercoppa Lazio-Juve ai raggi X: tutti i numeri della sfida|publisher=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|author1=Massimo Perrone|date=17 August 2013|accessdate=15 January 2018}}</ref> [[2003 Supercoppa Italiana|2003]]\n*[[UEFA Champions League]]: [[1995\u201396 UEFA Champions League|1995\u201396]]\n*[[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]]: [[1992\u201393 UEFA Cup|1992\u201393]]\n*[[UEFA Intertoto Cup]]: [[1999 UEFA Intertoto Cup|1999]]\n\n===Manager===\n'''Bari'''<ref name=\"uefa.com\"/>\n*[[Serie B]]: [[2008\u201309 Serie B|2008\u201309]]\n\n'''Juventus'''<ref name=\"uefa.com\"/>\n*[[Serie A]]: [[2011\u201312 Serie A|2011\u201312]], [[2012\u201313 Serie A|2012\u201313]], [[2013\u201314 Serie A|2013\u201314]]\n*[[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[2012 Supercoppa Italiana|2012]], [[2013 Supercoppa Italiana|2013]]\n\n'''Chelsea'''\n*[[Premier League]]: [[2016\u201317 Premier League|2016\u201317]]<ref name=PremProfile>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/managers/5556/Antonio-Conte/overview |title=Manager profile: Antonio Conte |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=19 September 2018}}</ref>\n*[[FA Cup]]: [[2017\u201318 FA Cup|2017\u201318]]<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/44091559 |title=Chelsea 1\u20130 Manchester United |first=Phil |last=McNulty |publisher=BBC Sport |date=19 May 2018 |accessdate=27 May 2018}}</ref>\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Panchina d'Oro|Panchina d'Argento]]: 2008\u201309<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gazzetta.it/Calcio/Squadre/Juventus/18-02-2013/panchina-d-oro-conte-premiata-impresa-la-juve-9261069240.shtml|title=Panchina d'oro a Conte Premiata l'impresa con la Juve|work=La Gazzetta dello Sport|language=Italian|first=Jacopo|last=Gerna|date=18 February 2013|accessdate=16 December 2015}}</ref>\n*[[Panchina d'Oro]]: [[2011\u201312 Serie A|2011\u201312]],<ref name=oro1>{{cite web|url=https://forzaitalianfootball.com/2013/01/gran-gala-del-calcio-2012-winners/|title=Gran Gala de