r of the Month]]: [[2016\u201317 Premier League#Monthly awards|October 2016]], November 2016, December 2016<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*London Football Awards for Manager of the Year: 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news/latest-news/2017/03/blues-honoured-at-london-football-awards.html?extcmp=SOCIA_TW_ENG_ARTICLES|title=Blues honoured at London Football Awards|publisher=Chelsea F.C.|accessdate=3 March 2017}}</ref>   \n*[[Premier League Manager of the Season]]: [[2016\u201317 Premier League#Annual awards|2016\u201317]]<ref name=PremProfile/>\n*[[LMA Manager of the Year]]: [[2016\u201317 Premier League|2016\u201317]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.leaguemanagers.com/news/lma-latest/antonio-conte-wins-lma-manager-year|title=Antonio Conte wins LMA Manager of the Year sponsored by Everest|publisher=League Managers Association|accessdate=23 May 2017}}</ref>\n*Special Achievement [[GQ]] Men of the Year Award: 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/sport/football/chelseas-antonio-conte-wins-special-award-at-2017-gq-men-of-the-year-gala-a3628186.html|title=Chelsea's Antonio Conte wins special award at 2017 GQ Men of the Year gala|publisher=EveningStandard|accessdate=6 September 2017}}</ref>\n*[[The Best FIFA Football Coach#Men.27s winners|The Best FIFA Men's Coach]] (2nd Place): [[The Best FIFA Football Awards 2017#The Best FIFA Men.27s Coach|2017]]<ref name=\"2017 The Best FIFA Men's Coach\">{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/the-best-fifa-football-awards/best-fifa-mens-coach/index.html|title=The Best FIFA Men's Coach|publisher=FIFA.com|accessdate=23 October 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Orders===\n:[[Image:Cavaliere OMRI BAR.svg|left|50px]] 5th Class / Knight: ''[[Italian orders of merit|Cavaliere Ordine al Merito della Repubblica Italiana]]: 2000<ref>{{cite web|title=ONORIFICENZE |url=http://www.quirinale.it/elementi/Onorificenze.aspx?pag=1558&qIdOnorificenza=&cognome=&nome=&daAnno=1800&aAnno=2015&luogoNascita=&testo=&ordinamento=2 |publisher=quirinale.it |